<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/styles.css">
    <title>Notebook Details</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="nav-bar">
        <a href="home.html">Home</a>
        <a href="upload.html">Upload</a>
        <a href="catalog.html" class="active">Catalog</a>
    </div>

    <div class="info-header">
        <p class="notebook-title">Team3Notebook.pdf</p>
        <div class="score-pill">80/100</div>
        <button class="download-btn">
            Download PDF 
            <img alt="download symbol" src="../graphics/download symbol.png" class="download-icon">
        </button>
    </div>

    <div class="dashboard-container">
        
        <div class="dashboard-top-row">
            
            <div class="top-left-column">
                <div class="dashboard-box summary-div">
                    <p><strong>Summary:</strong></p>
                    <p>This notebook covers the full design cycle of the robot, focusing on the intake mechanism and drivetrain iterations. It includes detailed sketches and CAD models.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flags-iterations-row">
                    <div class="dashboard-box flags-div">
                        <p class="box-title">&#9873; Flags for review:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Overly polished language (pg 37)</li>
                            <li>Sudden tone shift (pg 14)</li>
                            <li>Missing test data (pg 28)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dashboard-box iterations-div">
                        <p class="box-title">Number of Iterations:</p>
                        <p>Page Numbers:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>12-30</li>
                            <li>30-42</li>
                            <li>42-56</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="iteration-count">Three</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-box sections-div">
                <p class="box-title">Sections:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Problem definition & goals</li>
                    <li>Brainstorming</li>
                    <li>Design decisions</li>
                    <li>Iteration / redesign</li>
                    <li>Build and programming</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="box-title">Missing/Weak Sections:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li class="highlight-text">Testing and Results</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="box-title">Completeness Score: 80/100</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="dashboard-box questions-div">
            <p class="box-title">Interview Questions:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Why did you decide to do three iterations?</li>
                <li>How did you solve your programming and building issues?</li>
                <li>Why did you not document your testing and results?</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="dashboard-box design-process-div">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Engineering Design Process</th>
                    <th>Evidence Found</th>
                    <th>Confidence Level</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Identify the problem</td>
                    <td>Sets clear goals</td>
                    <td>Medium</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Brainstorming and Selection</td>
                    <td>3 design ideas with sketches</td>
                    <td>High</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Build the Solution</td>
                    <td>Various images and descriptions</td>
                    <td>Medium</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Testing & Repeat</td>
                    <td>Missing data points</td>
                    <td>Low</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
